{"id":18103,"date":"2022-12-31T04:32:36","date_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:32:36","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nd.wv3.net\/amg-car\/toyota-veloz-mitsubishi-xpander-dua-nhau-giam-gia-can-tet.html"},"modified":"2022-12-31T04:32:36","modified_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:32:36","slug":"toyota-veloz-mitsubishi-xpander-dua-nhau-giam-gia-can-tet","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/2022\/12\/31\/toyota-veloz-mitsubishi-xpander-dua-nhau-giam-gia-can-tet\/","title":{"rendered":"Toyota Veloz, Mitsubishi Xpander \u0111ua nhau gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 c\u1eadn T\u1ebft"},"content":{"rendered":"<\/p>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<p>\u0110\u1ea1i l\u00fd gi\u1ea3m 40 tri\u1ec7u cho Veloz \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ea3 h\u00e0ng, b\u00e1n ch\u1ea1y Xpander phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n AT Premium \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i 20 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\u01afu \u0111\u00e3i d\u00e0nh cho m\u1eabu MPV c\u1ee7a Toyota bao g\u1ed3m ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t kho\u1ea3ng 30 tri\u1ec7u v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n \u0111i k\u00e8m.  T\u00f9y t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd, n\u1ebfu kh\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 quy \u0111\u1ed5i ra ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7.  Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, do c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat v\u00e0 nhu c\u1ea7u cao h\u01a1n Veloz n\u00ean Mitsubishi Xpander c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i nh\u01b0ng \u00edt h\u01a1n.  \u0110\u1ea1i l\u00fd gi\u1ea3m 20 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng cho b\u1ea3n AT Premium b\u00e1n ch\u1ea1y nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Veloz t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd Toyota \u1edf TP.HCM.  \u1ea2nh: Ph\u1ea1m Trung\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/toyota-veloz-mitsubishi-xpander-dua-nhau-giam-gia-can-tet.jpg\" title=\"toyota-veloz-mitsubishi-xpander-dua-nhau-giam-gia-can-tet\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/toyota-veloz-mitsubishi-xpander-dua-nhau-giam-gia-can-tet-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/toyota-veloz-mitsubishi-xpander-dua-nhau-giam-gia-can-tet-600x360.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/toyota-veloz-mitsubishi-xpander-dua-nhau-giam-gia-can-tet.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Veloz t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd Toyota \u1edf TP.HCM.  \u1ea2nh: Ph\u1ea1m Trung <\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Theo nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean kinh doanh \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd Toyota, ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i n\u00e0y nh\u1eb1m th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y doanh s\u1ed1 v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft h\u00e0ng t\u1ed3n kho cho c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u trong n\u0103m.  Toyota chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1edf b\u00e1n l\u00f4 xe Veloz v\u00e0 Avanza l\u1eafp r\u00e1p trong n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2023. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Toyota Veloz sau th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m gi\u00e1, gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Veloz, Xpander, nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eabu xe kh\u00e1c trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac c\u0169ng gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 d\u1ecbp cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m.  Hyundai Stargazer gi\u1ea3m kho\u1ea3ng 20-30 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 50% l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1.  Suzuki XL7 gi\u1ea3m 20 tri\u1ec7u, Ertiga gi\u1ea3m 10 tri\u1ec7u ho\u1eb7c g\u00f3i ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n 15-18 tri\u1ec7u.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh th\u1ecb ph\u1ea7n \u1edf ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac MPV n\u0103m 2022 ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 gi\u1eefa Veloz v\u00e0 Xpander.  Veloz l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu xe b\u00e1n ch\u1ea1y nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Toyota t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u00f9 m\u1edbi ra m\u1eaft t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 3.  T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft th\u00e1ng 11, Veloz \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 12.876 xe, ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp sau Vios v\u00e0 Corolla Cross trong d\u1ea3i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ty Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.  X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac, Veloz \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 sau Mitsubishi Xpander.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Xpander AT Premium.  \u1ea2nh: Th\u00e0nh Nh\u00e2n\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421643_521_toyota-veloz-mitsubishi-xpander-dua-nhau-giam-gia-can-tet.jpg\" title=\"1672421643_521_toyota-veloz-mitsubishi-xpander-dua-nhau-giam-gia-can-tet\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421643_521_toyota-veloz-mitsubishi-xpander-dua-nhau-giam-gia-can-tet-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421643_521_toyota-veloz-mitsubishi-xpander-dua-nhau-giam-gia-can-tet-600x401.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672421643_521_toyota-veloz-mitsubishi-xpander-dua-nhau-giam-gia-can-tet.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Xpander AT Premium.  \u1ea2nh: Th\u00e0nh Nh\u00e2n <\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">C\u1ed9ng d\u1ed3n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2022 \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 11, Xpander b\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 20.217 xe, g\u1ea7n g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i Veloz.  T\u1ea1i l\u1ec5 trao gi\u1ea3i Car Awards 2022 do VnExpress t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, Mitsubishi Xpander l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 Xe c\u1ee7a n\u0103m ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac MPV.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">N\u0103m 2023, ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac xe \u0111a d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n khi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe (tr\u1eeb Suzuki XL7) \u0111\u1ec1u thu\u1ed9c th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t.  S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a hai m\u1eabu xe H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 Hyundai Stargazer v\u00e0 Kia Carens v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m 2022 c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o th\u00eam s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\">Ph\u1ea1m Trung<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>AMGCAR.VN<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/p><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u0110\u1ea1i l\u00fd gi\u1ea3m 40 tri\u1ec7u cho Veloz \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ea3 h\u00e0ng, b\u00e1n ch\u1ea1y Xpander phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n AT Premium \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i 20 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng. \u01afu \u0111\u00e3i d\u00e0nh cho m\u1eabu MPV c\u1ee7a Toyota bao g\u1ed3m ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t kho\u1ea3ng 30 tri\u1ec7u v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n \u0111i k\u00e8m. T\u00f9y t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd, n\u1ebfu kh\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 ph\u1ee5 [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":17616,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[75],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18103"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=18103"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18103\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/17616"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=18103"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=18103"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=18103"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{re